title: Stranger Doesn’t Believe Amy Is Her Son’s Mother + Lunchbox’s Wife Lays Down The Law On His Work Trip + David Lee Murphy and Dan+Shay Stop By
itunes:title: Stranger Doesn’t Believe Amy Is Her Son’s Mother + Lunchbox’s Wife Lays Down The Law On His Work Trip + David Lee Murphy and Dan+Shay Stop By
description:
A stranger didn’t believe that Amy was really her son’s mother. Lunchbox brings in audio of his wife’s response to him requesting to take a work trip the week after Baby Box will be born. Also, David Lee Murphy and Dan+Shay stop by the studio!
